@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<section class="section-block">
    <div class="container-fluid page-shell" style="max-width:760px">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p><em>Effective date: June 2026</em></p>

        <h2>Who we are</h2>
        <p>Hike Jordan is a hiking marketplace that aggregates organized hiking trips across Jordan. We connect visitors with verified independent organizers. Contact: <strong>hello@hikejordan.jo</strong></p>

        <h2>What data we collect</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Organizer accounts:</strong> name, email address, WhatsApp number, and region preferences provided during sign-up.</li>
            <li><strong>Hike listings:</strong> trip details submitted by approved organizers (title, description, date, price, location, capacity).</li>
            <li><strong>Authentication:</strong> encrypted session cookies stored in your browser to keep you signed in.</li>
            <li><strong>Server logs:</strong> IP address, browser type, pages visited, and timestamps — retained for 30 days for security and debugging.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How we use your data</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>To display hike listings to the public.</li>
            <li>To authenticate organizer and admin accounts.</li>
            <li>To moderate submitted listings and organizer profiles.</li>
            <li>To investigate security incidents or abuse.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not sell personal data. We do not share it with third parties except as required by Jordanian law.</p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use a single authentication cookie (<code>HikeJordan.Auth</code>) that is set only when you sign in. It expires after 8 hours of inactivity. No tracking or advertising cookies are used.</p>

        <h2>Data retention</h2>
        <p>Organizer account data is retained while the account is active. Server logs are retained for 30 days. You may request deletion of your account by emailing us.</p>

        <h2>Your rights</h2>
        <p>Under applicable law you have the right to access, correct, or delete personal data we hold about you. Send requests to <strong>hello@hikejordan.jo</strong>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>

        <h2>Security</h2>
        <p>Passwords are hashed using bcrypt before storage. All traffic is served over HTTPS. Sessions use secure, HTTP-only cookies. We apply security headers on every response.</p>

        <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>If we make material changes, we will update the effective date above. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>
    </div>
</section>
